<label>Jira Host</label>
<input id="jira-host" type="text" placeholder="mycompany.atlassian.net" />
<label>Server URL</label>
<input id="server-url" type="text" placeholder="http://localhost:3456" />
<div class="boards-list">
  <h2>Configured Boards</h2>
  <div id="boards-list"></div>
</div>
```

**No About Information Currently Provided:**
- No version information
- No help documentation
- No keyboard shortcuts list
- No feature descriptions

