Jiranimo is a **Chrome Extension + Node.js Backend** that brings AI-powered task automation to Jira. The board screen implementation uses vanilla JavaScript to inject badges on issues and manage real-time task synchronization via WebSocket. There are **no keyboard shortcuts** implemented currently, but a solid **modal/overlay pattern already exists** (used for board configuration). An **about/help overlay would be straightforward** to add following the existing modal pattern. No about page or help documentation currently exists in the extension.

